<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🎸 Dangerous Bros Pedalboard System</h1>
            <p>Phase 4: Web Application</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Welcome</h2>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <p>안녕하세요, <strong>
                            <%= user.name %>
                        </strong>님!</p>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/mypage" class="btn btn-primary">마이페이지</a>
                        <a href="/explorer" class="btn btn-secondary">페달보드 탐색</a>
                        <a href="/statistics" class="btn btn-secondary">통계 및 랭킹</a>
                        <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn" style="background-color: #ef4444; color: white;">로그아웃</a>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <p>페달보드 관리 시스템에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</p>
                        <div class="actions">
                            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">로그인</a>
                            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-secondary">회원가입</a>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2025 KNU Database Project Team 5</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>